{"tid":895540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(中國大撒幣) 贊比亞反殖民遊行  中國人商店被衝擊","createTime":"2018-11-09T09:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T10:46:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"88bc35f1544f0f048e22d03957ee00c2f7179708","tid":895540,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2062618/org/4cd4183fc957bdd13d6badeb2d865bb2.jpeg/Tmfoap4gmByx4aTKWsufnWzqmi3IJH5DKzqiOCs6ojg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2062618%2Forg%2F4cd4183fc957bdd13d6badeb2d865bb2.jpeg%2FTmfoap4gmByx4aTKWsufnWzqmi3IJH5DKzqiOCs6ojg&h=384c2a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因有傳聞稱贊比亞政府要將林業公司出售給中資，贊比亞銅帶省基特韋市日前出現針對中國人的騷亂和遊行。數家中國人經營的商舖被洗劫或打砸，不過目前並無中國人受傷。據稱已經有至少151名參與騷亂者被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2062620/org/3beaa37b51c3f746d69205e6b1e7787a.jpeg/DJGQhJkZMDJRcZ6LC-psrLbVpxQKTzMKbTl5tm05ebY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2062620%2Forg%2F3beaa37b51c3f746d69205e6b1e7787a.jpeg%2FDJGQhJkZMDJRcZ6LC-psrLbVpxQKTzMKbTl5tm05ebY&h=080ebc5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國駐贊比亞使館6日在使館網站發布安全提醒，要求銅帶省基特韋市區的中資企業、中國公民近期加強安全防範。<br />\n<br />\n使館提醒說，發生小規模騷亂和遊行主要原因是一些當地人聽信「政府把贊比亞林業公司出售給中國人」的傳言，聚眾鬧事，數家中國商店遭到打劫，蒙受較為嚴重的物資和財產損失。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，中國駐贊比亞使館與贊有關部門聯繫交涉，使館提醒在基特韋市區的中國公民避免前往當地人聚集的地區，密切注意事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n使館領保聯絡員表示，5日上午，有人在基特韋點燃輪胎，攔截、拍打過往車輛，基特韋市兩家中國人經營的商店遭洗劫，一家中國人經營的商店玻璃被砸碎。另有數家中國商店和企業被當地民眾圍住，當地華僑華人團體及時聯繫防暴警察，使這些商店和企業未遭打砸、搶劫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2062619/org/de2cfee09e7b7a750932232151792e9a.jpeg/PsAwlff0urcy7yf3cM4EShVwFpYRaE1KX5CCgF-QgoA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2062619%2Forg%2Fde2cfee09e7b7a750932232151792e9a.jpeg%2FPsAwlff0urcy7yf3cM4EShVwFpYRaE1KX5CCgF-QgoA&h=b86c33b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n贊比亞政府指責反對派造謠<br />\n<br />\n贊比亞國家電視台稱，5日當天共有151名參與騷亂者被捕，沒有出現中國人傷亡的情況。<br />\n<br />\n贊比亞信息與廣播部長、政府首席發言人朵拉&middot;西利亞表示，政府沒有出售贊比亞林業公司，也未與任何投資者洽談收購。有關謠言來自「反對派製造的假新聞」。<br />\n<br />\n贊比亞總統新聞和公共關係特別助理阿莫斯&middot;錢達說，總統倫古對有人散佈針對中國人的仇外信息感到失望，已指示警方調查此事。<br />\n<br />\n（新華網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/255998/%E5%82%B3%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E6%9E%97%E6%A5%AD%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%94%AE%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87-%E8%B4%8A%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E5%8F%8D%E8%8F%AF%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82-%E6%95%B8%E5%AE%B6%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E8%A2%AB%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F255998%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%2594%25AE%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25B3%2587-%25E8%25B4%258A%25E6%25AF%2594%25E4%25BA%259E%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25BA%2597%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25A1%259D%25E6%2593%258A&d=VgGdjm0gORkSc%2F0wb7u1sMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=7ef38210\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/255998/%E5%82%B3%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E6%9E%97%E6%A5%AD%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%94%AE%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87-%E8%B4%8A%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E5%8F%8D%E8%8F%AF%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82-%E6%95%B8%E5%AE%B6%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E8%A2%AB%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A</a>"},{"pid":"e46178bee162f764199f53b346fc94bc6e6e476a","tid":895540,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T09:36:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f4ecac760c9d02e15d0417c5df00c882d305db8","tid":895540,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e32761a466bf95fc4714fddfa97acd3052eb04d","tid":895540,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:46:00.000Z","msg":"傻閪支那狗，連土人都恰鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}